<p>And does not recursively visit the body of the try statement, the catch =
body, or the finalizer statements.</p>

<p>To fix this major issue in many of deno_lint=E2=80=99s rules it would ha=
ve to change every single visit function on every rule to include recursive=
ly visiting the children manually.</p>

